{
  "version": 1,
  "device_id_resolution": "preferred_label",
  "_notes": [
    "Copy this file to automation-rules.json in the repo/server root (same directory as domesti-bot.config.json).",
    "settings_location.lat/lon are the configured home point (maps, astronomical schedules, and distance features such as vacation mode). Do not use a geofence center as a substitute. lat=0 and lon=0 together mean home is not configured.",
    "users_min_distance_from_home_m is true when every listed user_id has a usable GPS location at least min_distance_m from settings_location home (AND across users; missing/low-accuracy locations fail closed).",
    "device_id values are tile/REPL display names; the evaluator resolves them to Kasa hosts, Sonos zone labels, Vizio TV labels, or Tailwind door ids.",
    "Geofence ids must match Automations → Geofences (house is typical for home; west-point for West Point).",
    "Edge-triggered rules that use geofence conditions (users_inside_geofence / users_outside_geofence) rely on accuracy_edge_grace_s (default 120 s). Poor horizontal GPS accuracy can block enter/leave edges without grace; the evaluator also reconciles sustained GPS inside/outside streaks after 10 min.",
    "SMTP must be configured under Automations → Mail for notification emails to send.",
    "vacation_mode (optional top-level block; also editable under Automations → Vacation) is a sticky latch: when enabled, arms after all user_ids stay ≥ min_distance_m from settings_location home for hysteresis_s (default 1800), and disarms when any of those users is inside the home geofence (wifi_home_geofence_id or geofences containing home lat/lon). Being closer than min_distance_m without entering the home geofence does not disarm. Without a resolvable home geofence the latch will not arm, and if already armed it fail-safe disarms. notify_on_transition (default true) emails notification_emails on arm/disarm edges; anomaly device emails while armed are separate (#464). Persists armed + far_since across restart. Leave enabled false in the example; operator wiring is local (#465).",
    "Rule 1 fires when Henrique OR Kristen enters house after sunset (arrival edge, not merely present at sunset).",
    "Rule 2 (evening-lights-off-both-home) runs every 10 min after sunset: when both have been home 10+ min and either arrival light is still on, turn both off.",
    "Rule 3 (evening-interior-lights-on-anyone-home) uses triggers [edge_true, scheduled] and arms from 25 min before sunset until midnight: at the window open it evaluates once — if Henrique OR Kristen is already home, interior lamps turn on; otherwise the next home geofence enter by either person fires the rule (once per local day). Not a periodic poll.",
    "Rule 4 (away-shutdown-everyone-outside-20m) runs every 10 min: when Henrique AND Kristen have been outside house 20+ min and any listed light/media device is still on, turn them off (garage doors are not closed).",
    "Rule 5 (away-garage-open-alert) uses dwell_satisfied: when both have been outside house 20+ min and a watched garage door has been open 20+ min, email operator@example.com and resident@example.com (once per away episode).",
    "Rule 6 (morning-master-bedroom-fan-off) runs daily at 7:30am: when Master Bedroom fan is on, turn it off and email operator@example.com.",
    "Rule 7 (daylight-master-bedroom-fan-on-alert) uses device_state trigger only: during astronomical daylight (sunrise to sunset), email operator@example.com when Master Bedroom fan turns on.",
    "Optional device_actions.delay_s (int seconds, 0–86400): omit or 0 = run on rule fire; >0 schedules that action for fire_time + delay_s. Pending delayed actions are persisted in SQLite (rule_deferred_device_actions) and reloaded on startup, so a follow-up still runs after a process restart during the delay window; they are cancelled if the rule is deleted or disabled before the delay elapses. notify_on_fire / cooldown / fire_once_per_local_day apply to the rule fire, not each delayed step.",
    "Rule 8 (hdhomerun-nightly-power-cycle, enabled false in the example) shows a sequenced Kasa power cycle: turn_off at 4am cron, then turn_on after delay_s=60."
  ],
  "settings_location": {
    "lat": 41.194072,
    "lon": -73.8883254,
    "timezone": "America/New_York",
    "home_label": "Home",
    "wifi_home_presence_enabled": true,
    "wifi_home_geofence_id": "house"
  },
  "vacation_mode": {
    "enabled": false,
    "user_ids": ["user-a", "user-b"],
    "min_distance_m": 80000,
    "hysteresis_s": 1800,
    "min_location_accuracy_m": 50,
    "notification_emails": ["operator@example.com"],
    "notify_on_transition": true
  },
  "rules": [
    {
      "id": "evening-arrival-home-lights",
      "label": "Evening arrival — front + garage lights",
      "enabled": true,
      "triggers": ["edge_true"],
      "cooldown_s": 300,
      "min_location_accuracy_m": 50,
      "accuracy_edge_grace_s": 120,
      "notify_on_fire": true,
      "notification_emails": ["automation@example.com"],
      "conditions": {
        "all": [
          {
            "type": "after_sunset",
            "offset_minutes": 0,
            "window_end": "midnight"
          },
          {
            "type": "any",
            "conditions": [
              {
                "type": "users_inside_geofence",
                "geofence_id": "house",
                "user_ids": ["henrique"]
              },
              {
                "type": "users_inside_geofence",
                "geofence_id": "house",
                "user_ids": ["kristen"]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "device_actions": [
        {
          "family_id": "kasa",
          "device_id": "Front door lights",
          "action": "turn_on"
        },
        {
          "family_id": "kasa",
          "device_id": "Garage",
          "action": "turn_on"
        },
        {
          "family_id": "kasa",
          "device_id": "Garage outside lights",
          "action": "turn_on"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "evening-lights-off-both-home",
      "label": "Turn off arrival lights when both home 10+ min after sunset",
      "enabled": true,
      "triggers": ["scheduled"],
      "schedule_cron": "*/10 * * * *",
      "cooldown_s": 300,
      "min_location_accuracy_m": 50,
      "accuracy_edge_grace_s": 120,
      "notify_on_fire": false,
      "conditions": {
        "all": [
          {
            "type": "after_sunset",
            "offset_minutes": 0,
            "window_end": "midnight"
          },
          {
            "type": "users_inside_geofence_for_s",
            "geofence_id": "house",
            "user_ids": ["henrique", "kristen"],
            "min_inside_s": 600
          },
          {
            "type": "devices_any_in_state",
            "state": "on",
            "devices": [
              {
                "family_id": "kasa",
                "device_id": "Front door lights"
              },
              {
                "family_id": "kasa",
                "device_id": "Garage outside lights"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "device_actions": [
        {
          "family_id": "kasa",
          "device_id": "Front door lights",
          "action": "turn_off"
        },
        {
          "family_id": "kasa",
          "device_id": "Garage outside lights",
          "action": "turn_off"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "evening-interior-lights-on-anyone-home",
      "label": "Turn on interior lamps on evening home arrival (25 min before sunset to midnight, once per day)",
      "enabled": true,
      "triggers": ["edge_true", "scheduled"],
      "fire_once_per_local_day": true,
      "cooldown_s": 300,
      "min_location_accuracy_m": 50,
      "accuracy_edge_grace_s": 120,
      "notify_on_fire": false,
      "conditions": {
        "all": [
          {
            "type": "after_sunset",
            "offset_minutes": -25,
            "window_end": "midnight"
          },
          {
            "type": "any",
            "conditions": [
              {
                "type": "users_inside_geofence",
                "geofence_id": "house",
                "user_ids": ["henrique"]
              },
              {
                "type": "users_inside_geofence",
                "geofence_id": "house",
                "user_ids": ["kristen"]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "device_actions": [
        {
          "family_id": "kasa",
          "device_id": "Kitchen lamp",
          "action": "turn_on"
        },
        {
          "family_id": "kasa",
          "device_id": "Living room lamp",
          "action": "turn_on"
        },
        {
          "family_id": "kasa",
          "device_id": "Living room lamp2",
          "action": "turn_on"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "away-shutdown-everyone-outside-20m",
      "label": "Turn off lights and media when everyone away 20+ min",
      "enabled": true,
      "triggers": ["scheduled"],
      "schedule_cron": "*/10 * * * *",
      "cooldown_s": 300,
      "min_location_accuracy_m": 50,
      "notify_on_fire": false,
      "conditions": {
        "all": [
          {
            "type": "users_outside_geofence_for_s",
            "geofence_id": "house",
            "user_ids": ["henrique", "kristen"],
            "min_outside_s": 1200
          },
          {
            "type": "devices_any_in_state",
            "state": "on",
            "devices": [
              { "family_id": "kasa", "device_id": "Front door lights" },
              { "family_id": "kasa", "device_id": "Garage" },
              { "family_id": "kasa", "device_id": "Garage outside lights" },
              { "family_id": "kasa", "device_id": "Kitchen lamp" },
              { "family_id": "kasa", "device_id": "Living room lamp" },
              { "family_id": "kasa", "device_id": "Living room lamp2" },
              { "family_id": "sonos", "device_id": "Kitchen" },
              { "family_id": "sonos", "device_id": "Living Room" },
              { "family_id": "sonos", "device_id": "Master Bedroom" },
              { "family_id": "vizio", "device_id": "Kitchen TV" }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "device_actions": [
        { "family_id": "kasa", "device_id": "Front door lights", "action": "turn_off" },
        { "family_id": "kasa", "device_id": "Garage", "action": "turn_off" },
        { "family_id": "kasa", "device_id": "Garage outside lights", "action": "turn_off" },
        { "family_id": "kasa", "device_id": "Kitchen lamp", "action": "turn_off" },
        { "family_id": "kasa", "device_id": "Living room lamp", "action": "turn_off" },
        { "family_id": "kasa", "device_id": "Living room lamp2", "action": "turn_off" },
        { "family_id": "sonos", "device_id": "Kitchen", "action": "pause" },
        { "family_id": "sonos", "device_id": "Living Room", "action": "pause" },
        { "family_id": "sonos", "device_id": "Master Bedroom", "action": "pause" },
        { "family_id": "vizio", "device_id": "Kitchen TV", "action": "turn_off" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "away-garage-open-alert",
      "label": "Email when a garage door is open and everyone away 20+ min",
      "enabled": true,
      "triggers": ["dwell_satisfied"],
      "cooldown_s": 0,
      "min_location_accuracy_m": 50,
      "notify_on_fire": true,
      "notification_emails": [
        "operator@example.com",
        "resident@example.com"
      ],
      "conditions": {
        "all": [
          {
            "type": "users_outside_geofence_for_s",
            "geofence_id": "house",
            "user_ids": ["henrique", "kristen"],
            "min_outside_s": 1200
          },
          {
            "type": "devices_any_in_state_for_s",
            "state": "open",
            "min_duration_s": 1200,
            "devices": [
              { "family_id": "tailwind", "device_id": "Left" },
              { "family_id": "tailwind", "device_id": "Right" }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "device_actions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "kristen-west-point-arrive",
      "label": "Kristen arrived at West Point",
      "enabled": true,
      "triggers": ["edge_true"],
      "cooldown_s": 120,
      "min_location_accuracy_m": 50,
      "notify_on_fire": true,
      "notification_emails": ["automation@example.com"],
      "conditions": {
        "all": [
          {
            "type": "users_inside_geofence",
            "geofence_id": "west-point",
            "user_ids": ["kristen"]
          }
        ]
      },
      "device_actions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "kristen-west-point-leave",
      "label": "Kristen left West Point",
      "enabled": true,
      "triggers": ["edge_true"],
      "cooldown_s": 120,
      "min_location_accuracy_m": 50,
      "notify_on_fire": true,
      "notification_emails": ["automation@example.com"],
      "conditions": {
        "all": [
          {
            "type": "users_outside_geofence",
            "geofence_id": "west-point",
            "user_ids": ["kristen"]
          }
        ]
      },
      "device_actions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "morning-master-bedroom-fan-off",
      "label": "Turn off master bedroom fan at 7:30am if on",
      "enabled": true,
      "triggers": ["scheduled"],
      "schedule_cron": "30 7 * * *",
      "cooldown_s": 300,
      "min_location_accuracy_m": 50,
      "notify_on_fire": true,
      "notification_emails": ["operator@example.com"],
      "conditions": {
        "all": [
          {
            "type": "devices_any_in_state",
            "state": "on",
            "devices": [
              { "family_id": "kasa", "device_id": "Master Bedroom fan" }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "device_actions": [
        {
          "family_id": "kasa",
          "device_id": "Master Bedroom fan",
          "action": "turn_off"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "daylight-master-bedroom-fan-on-alert",
      "label": "Email when master bedroom fan turns on during daylight",
      "enabled": true,
      "triggers": ["device_state"],
      "cooldown_s": 1800,
      "min_location_accuracy_m": 50,
      "notify_on_fire": true,
      "notification_emails": ["operator@example.com"],
      "conditions": {
        "all": [
          { "type": "daylight" },
          {
            "type": "devices_any_in_state",
            "state": "on",
            "devices": [
              { "family_id": "kasa", "device_id": "Master Bedroom fan" }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "device_actions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "hdhomerun-nightly-power-cycle",
      "label": "Nightly HDHomeRun tuner power cycle",
      "enabled": false,
      "triggers": ["scheduled"],
      "schedule_cron": "0 4 * * *",
      "cooldown_s": 300,
      "fire_once_per_local_day": true,
      "min_location_accuracy_m": 50,
      "notify_on_fire": false,
      "notification_emails": [],
      "conditions": {
        "all": []
      },
      "device_actions": [
        {
          "family_id": "kasa",
          "device_id": "HDHomeRun tuner",
          "action": "turn_off"
        },
        {
          "family_id": "kasa",
          "device_id": "HDHomeRun tuner",
          "action": "turn_on",
          "delay_s": 60
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
